<DATELINE>HONG KONG (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A Vietnamese delegation arrived Friday to help
arrange the first large-scale repatriation of boat people willing to
return home.
   It was the first time a delegation from Hanoi has visited this
British colony.
