General Electric, down ] at 46|; American Express, down | at 30|,
and Philip Morris, down 1\ at 108.
   The NYSE's composite index of all its listed common stocks fell
1.18 to 164.95. At the American Stock Exchange, the market value
index was down 1.79 at 323.57.
   Volume on the Big Board came to 124.04 million shares with two
